data.description: HUGE MARKET PRICE ADJUSTMENT!!  This amazing 4 bedroom, 3 bath, 2 car garage POOL HOME is waiting for your finishing touches. With a BRAND NEW ROOF, NEW A/C, new back flow system, and new electric garage door opener, you'll have peace of mind living for years to come!! Boasting cathedral ceilings, split floor plan, completely FENCED IN back yard, indoor laundry, screened in lanai, fire pit, as well as stainless steel appliances, your new home will be a great place to relax or entertain friends and family. Close to everything including beaches, shopping, restaurants, golf, a new water park, Warm Mineral Springs, world class fishing, 3 spring training facilities (Reds, Rays, and Braves), and much more!! Call today for your private showing!!
